As Dachande reached Red Bolt, Freewing turned a corner in the ruined base. 
"Enough computer equipment to supply us for a few years." Freewing said. He 
pulled some rope out of his side and tied the computer equipment together, 
and began dragging it to the shore line.

--part1_69.10622daf.27a5c135_boundary
